<ab facs="#facs_102_r2l28">vier halbe tuche in <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> groͣen
            v̈mbſlag / vnd maine daʒ die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r2l29">anderlewte ſein <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> / Nu hat der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan> die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
