            behabt / daʒ die ſein vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r2l31"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſein Alſo daʒ khein auſʒman
