<ab facs="#facs_102_r2l32">gemaine daran hab / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr
            von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchicken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r2l33">vnd beſtellen vvöllet / daʒ dem
              <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeine </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r2l34">tuche vvıder werden / Als etc das
              <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
