</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_102" id="50v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Cristan Wolczhofer,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie <add>man</add> im nu newlich czu Landshute in Urban
            Fünsingers herberg <add>aufgehalten</add>
<add>hab</add> vier gancze und vier halbe tuche in <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> groͣen
            ümbslag und maine, daz die anderlewte sein <expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu hat der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan> die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> seine tuch vor uns
            czu den <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> behabt, daz die sein und
              <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sein, also daz khein auszman
              <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemaine daran hab.
              <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> schicken und bestellen wöllet, daz dem
                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine tuche wider werden, als etc. Das
                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan> jubilate. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Lanshute <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
